Two adult Earth Fiends.

22
00:02:57,562 --> 00:02:59,002
We're no match for them.

23
00:02:59,242 --> 00:03:00,282
Find a way out now.

24
00:03:01,481 --> 00:03:02,402
I'll hold them off.

25
00:03:08,842 --> 00:03:09,682
This way!

26
00:03:09,721 --> 00:03:10,522
Luo, Yu Rong,

27
00:03:10,721 --> 00:03:11,921
