28
00:03:12,481 --> 00:03:13,122
Let's go.

29
00:03:13,122 --> 00:03:13,921
Hurry!

30
00:03:17,562 --> 00:03:18,721
Quick, get inside.

31
00:03:21,161 --> 00:03:21,842
Hurry.

32
00:03:22,242 --> 00:03:23,082
You go ahead.

33
00:03:23,721 --> 00:03:24,441
I'll cover you.

34
00:03:25,441 --> 00:03:25,962
Go.

35
00:03:25,962 --> 00:03:26,601
Be careful.

36
00:03:41,441 --> 00:03:44,082
- Third!
- Third!

37
00:03:44,082 --> 00:03:46,362
- Third!
- Third!

38
00:04:36,281 --> 00:04:37,841
Once entering the Twilight Chasm,

39
00:04:38,722 --> 00:04:40,162
fiends become human demons,

40
00:04:40,682 --> 00:04:42,122
and humans become fiendish wraiths.

41
00:05:10,482 --> 00:05:11,441
It's a dead end.

42
00:05:11,482 --> 00:05:12,521
This is the only exit.

43
00:05:15,961 --> 00:05:17,441
To deal with us,

44
00:05:17,881 --> 00:05:20,401
you even summoned
the ancestral Earth Demons.

45
00:05:22,881 --> 00:05:23,602
Fine then.

46
00:05:24,602 --> 00:05:27,002
Let's settle all scores at once.

47
00:05:28,562 --> 00:05:29,441
What's she saying?

48
00:05:31,408 --> 00:05:33,840
The underworld is where fiends dwell.

49
00:05:35,281 --> 00:05:39,602
Lurking beneath Turquoise Land,
they heed the ocarina's call.

50
00:05:40,401 --> 00:05:43,441
War Ocarina
has five tones and eight sounds.

51
00:05:44,641 --> 00:05:47,441
It governs heaven and earth
with the Dao as its score.

52
00:05:47,961 --> 00:05:52,081
Humans and fiends share paths,
merging into South Mountain.

53
00:05:52,841 --> 00:05:53,841
Were those Earth Demons

54
00:05:54,641 --> 00:05:55,521
summoned by you?

55
00:06:02,401 --> 00:06:05,201
I wanted to increase
our odds of success.

56
00:06:05,881 --> 00:06:06,922
But I never expected

57
00:06:07,081 --> 00:06:08,362
our South Mountain elders

58
00:06:08,961 --> 00:06:10,562
couldn't tell friend from foe.

59
00:06:15,984 --> 00:06:17,776
None of this matters now.

60
00:06:17,776 --> 00:06:19,362
Seven hounds, two whips, and one blade.

61
00:06:19,441 --> 00:06:21,401
If ten of us fight one fiend,
we stand a chance.

62
00:06:21,401 --> 00:06:23,216
But now it's two fiends
against seven of us.

63
00:06:23,216 --> 00:06:23,952
What do we do?

64
00:06:25,042 --> 00:06:25,841
Fight to the death.

65
00:06:26,562 --> 00:06:28,081
Killing even one would count as a win.

66
00:06:28,761 --> 00:06:30,321
There's only this one exit anyway.

67
00:06:31,881 --> 00:06:32,841
Let's take them on.

68
00:06:34,881 --> 00:06:35,562
Xing Shen,

69
00:06:36,922 --> 00:06:37,641
give the order.

70
00:06:39,761 --> 00:06:41,961
Wu Qing, watch Quecha.

71
00:06:42,722 --> 00:06:43,362
Yu Rong,

72
00:06:44,281 --> 00:06:46,002
hold off the big one
at the cave entrance.

73
00:06:46,722 --> 00:06:47,961
We'll break out together.

74
00:06:56,761 --> 00:06:57,401
Luo!

75
00:06:57,401 --> 00:06:58,042
Luo!

76
00:07:00,562 --> 00:07:01,362
What did you eat?

77
00:07:04,881 --> 00:07:05,761
It doesn't matter.

78
00:07:13,482 --> 00:07:14,362
Mad Blade medicine.

79
00:07:19,401 --> 00:07:20,362
Luo?

80
00:07:24,961 --> 00:07:25,641
Luo?

81
00:07:40,122 --> 00:07:41,122
Luo!

